而今天，德語和法語則是西方世界最重要的第二外語（英語則作爲最重要的第一外語） <ref name="eurobarometer2">{{cite web|title=Special Eurobarometer 386: Europeans and their languages|url=http://ec.europa.eu/public_opinion/archives/ebs/ebs_386_en.pdf|accessdate=2015-07-24|date=June 2012|publisher=European Commission|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106183351/http://ec.europa.eu/public_opinion/archives/ebs/ebs_386_en.pdf|archivedate=2016-01-06|type=report|}}</ref><ref name="goethe-institut">{{cite web|title=Deutsch als Fremdsprache weltweit. Datenerhebung 2015 – Worldwide survey of people learning German; conducted by the German Ministry for Foreign Affairs and the Goethe Institute|url=https://www.goethe.de/resources/files/pdf37/Bro_Deutschlernerhebung_final3.pdf|accessdate=4 July 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525142613/https://www.goethe.de/resources/files/pdf37/Bro_Deutschlernerhebung_final3.pdf|archivedate=25 May 2017|}}</ref>。德語及法語是歐盟<ref name="eurobarometer3">{{cite web|title=Special Eurobarometer 386: Europeans and their languages|url=http://ec.europa.eu/public_opinion/archives/ebs/ebs_386_en.pdf|accessdate=2015-07-24|date=June 2012|publisher=European Commission|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106183351/http://ec.europa.eu/public_opinion/archives/ebs/ebs_386_en.pdf|archivedate=2016-01-06|type=report|}}</ref>及俄羅斯<ref name="Levada2008">{{cite web|url=http://www.levada.ru/16-09-2008/znanie-inostrannykh-yazykov-v-rossii|accessdate=10 May 2015|date=16 September 2008|publisher=Levada Centre|language=ru|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510133101/http://www.levada.ru/16-09-2008/znanie-inostrannykh-yazykov-v-rossii|archivedate=10 May 2015|script-title=ru:Знание иностранных языков в России|trans-title=Knowledge of foreign languages in Russia|}}</ref>除英語外最爲人所知的外語。若論學習人數，德語在歐盟排行第三（在英語和法語之後）<ref name="eurostat">{{cite web|title=Foreign language learning statistics – Statistics Explained|url=http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Foreign_language_learning_statistics|accessdate=4 July 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170628100813/http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Foreign_language_learning_statistics|archivedate=28 June 2017|website=ec.europa.eu|}}</ref>，在美國亦排行第三（在西班牙語和法語之後）<ref>{{cite web|title=Foreign Language Enrollments in K–12 Public Schools|url=http://www.actfl.org/sites/default/files/pdfs/ReportSummary2011.pdf|date=February 2011|publisher=American Council on the Teaching of Foreign Languages (ACTFL)|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408184754/http://www.actfl.org/sites/default/files/pdfs/ReportSummary2011.pdf|archivedate=April 8, 2016|access-date=October 17, 2015|}}</ref><ref name="MLA">[[Modern_Language_Association|Modern Language Association]], February 2015, [http://www.mla.org/pdf/2013_enrollment_survey.pdf Enrollments in Languages Other Than English in United States Institutions of Higher Education, Fall 2013] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404015237/http://www.mla.org/pdf/2013_enrollment_survey.pdf|date=2015-04-04}}. Retrieved 2015-07-07.</ref>。2015年，全球有1540人學習德語<ref name="goethe-institut2">{{cite web|title=Deutsch als Fremdsprache weltweit. Datenerhebung 2015 – Worldwide survey of people learning German; conducted by the German Ministry for Foreign Affairs and the Goethe Institute|url=https://www.goethe.de/resources/files/pdf37/Bro_Deutschlernerhebung_final3.pdf|accessdate=4 July 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525142613/https://www.goethe.de/resources/files/pdf37/Bro_Deutschlernerhebung_final3.pdf|archivedate=25 May 2017|}}</ref>，該數字自2005年就維持穩定，上下變化幅度不超過100萬。全球共有7500萬至1億人口能夠以德語對話。<ref name="Ammon, 20145">[http://www.ulrichammon.de/resources/Stellung_der_deutschen_Sprache.pdf Ammon, Ulrich – Die Stellung der deutschen Sprache in der Welt] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109200453/http://www.ulrichammon.de/resources/Stellung_der_deutschen_Sprache.pdf|date=2015-11-09}} (de Gruyter Mouton; {{ISBN|978-3-11-019298-8}})</ref>根據2012年的調查顯示，歐盟有4700人（佔全球德語外語人口的2/3）宣稱擁有一定的德語水準。德語還是中歐和北歐最多人學習的外語，包括[[捷克|捷克]]、[[克罗地亚|克罗地亚]]、[[丹麦|丹麦]]、[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]、[[斯洛伐克|斯洛伐克]]、[[斯洛文尼亞|斯洛文尼亞]]、[[瑞典|瑞典]]和[[波兰|波蘭]]。<ref name="eurobarometer4">{{cite web|title=Special Eurobarometer 386: Europeans and their languages|url=http://ec.europa.eu/public_opinion/archives/ebs/ebs_386_en.pdf|accessdate=2015-07-24|date=June 2012|publisher=European Commission|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106183351/http://ec.europa.eu/public_opinion/archives/ebs/ebs_386_en.pdf|archivedate=2016-01-06|type=report|}}</ref><ref name="eurostat2">{{cite web|title=Foreign language learning statistics – Statistics Explained|url=http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Foreign_language_learning_statistics|accessdate=4 July 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170628100813/http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Foreign_language_learning_statistics|archivedate=28 June 2017|website=ec.europa.eu|}}</ref>

